originalText.text: If i can give less of a star, I definitely would. This place is an absolute disaster. One of the workers here is extremely nasty, disrespectful, and unprofessional. I wish I would’ve taken his name down. I lost my ticket and gave them very specific details about everything they needed to know. I then wait for this man for over an hour for him to bring my car up. He comes back to then tell me he needs my license and can’t explain to me why he needs my license. I show him a picture of my license and he proceeds to scan it to then tells me it’s not working and I need to figure it out and I am not getting my car because he needs to go home. On top of that, their prices are absolutely outrageous and overpriced. No reason someone should be paying so much to park their car for only a few hours especially when you’re receiving such awful service. Super nasty man and I hope nobody has to interact with him and encounter his disgusting attitude and rudeness. This place needs to get shut down, I can’t further explain how terrible EVERYTHING here.
